  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An Animated Gorefest Where You Take on a Serial Killer!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abducted and tied up in a basement by a psychopathic serial killer, it's up to you to turn the tables on this crazy freak and find all the ways to kill him in the most brutal and bizarre ways.<br><br><strong>Featuring the Most Crazy Torture Methods from History!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What better way to take revenge on a serial killer than using his barbaric devices against him? In Whack the Serial Killer there's a whole range of crazy methods from the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764990/extras/7e4617ad1da5711c43186b885813e350.avif?t=1751855118\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764990/extras_big/7e4617ad1da5711c43186b885813e350.avif?t=1751855118 width=800 height=514 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><strong>3 Previous Chapters Also Included Making 4 Games in Total!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>All 3 previous entertaining whack games optimised for HD play and included for free with Whack the Serial Killer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764990/extras/5948602ec4c72a1a01a48b27d4e4d83a.avif?t=1751855118\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764990/extras_big/5948602ec4c72a1a01a48b27d4e4d83a.avif?t=1751855118 width=800 height=226 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Warning!* These games aren't for everyone, but for those who love bloody animations and crazy creative kills all four are the perfect way to spend a small amount of your day.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An Animated Gorefest Where You Take on a Serial Killer!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abducted and tied up in a basement by a psychopathic serial killer, it's up to you to turn the tables on this crazy freak and find all the ways to kill him in the most brutal and bizarre ways.<br><br><strong>Featuring the Most Crazy Torture Methods from History!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What better way to take revenge on a serial killer than using his barbaric devices against him? In Whack the Serial Killer there's a whole range of crazy methods from the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764990/extras/7e4617ad1da5711c43186b885813e350.avif?t=1751855118\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764990/extras_big/7e4617ad1da5711c43186b885813e350.avif?t=1751855118 width=800 height=514 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><strong>3 Previous Chapters Also Included Making 4 Games in Total!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>All 3 previous entertaining whack games optimised for HD play and included for free with Whack the Serial Killer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764990/extras/5948602ec4c72a1a01a48b27d4e4d83a.avif?t=1751855118\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/764990/extras_big/5948602ec4c72a1a01a48b27d4e4d83a.avif?t=1751855118 width=800 height=226 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Warning!* These games aren't for everyone, but for those who love bloody animations and crazy creative kills all four are the perfect way to spend a small amount of your day.</p>",
